{"tid":395634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為$500帶毒 品學兼優女生毁前途","createTime":"2017-09-11T03:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T04:40:10.000Z","uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be6b708a100ea47423a88af17fe72adc3ade082e","tid":395634,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"不法分子招攬青少年販毒或攜帶違禁品的情況令人關注，有品學兼優女學生僅收取500元酬勞便幫人帶毒，前途盡毁。有警方學校聯絡主任指，有畢業生誤入歧途後再物色學弟學妹帶貨，警方除在學校附近加強巡邏，亦希望透過到學校辦講座，提升青少年的防罪意識。<br />\n今年上半年逾1,400名10至20歲青少年被捕，較去年同期減少逾2成，但干犯輕微毒品案被捕人數則上升逾1成，有59人，涉及嚴重毒品罪行而被捕的青少年則有118人，主要涉及冰毒、海洛英及可卡因，近月涉大麻的案件亦趨升。"},{"pid":"aa4ac1588b48a95130b2bf3017276fe3abf040d0","tid":395634,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"多麼蠢的妞.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4ba31473ba0460d1aeb2b99f71beae0f1f1491","tid":395634,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲女拜託唔好生下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢下一代連呼吸都唔知識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢知唔知啲毒品市值幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 500蚊就同人帶. 出嚟做雞都唔只搵咁少啦. 死撚咗佢啦"},{"pid":"6cc98f950055b6e3bebe85e98b5faa913178a07e","tid":395634,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲女拜託唔好生下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢下一代連呼吸都唔知識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢知唔知啲毒品市值幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 500蚊就同人帶. 出嚟做雞都唔只搵咁少啦. 死撚咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n搵佢帶個班又係<br />\n幾百萬毒品 搵個$500兼職幫你運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0903b9685af3d0c95d048948554d67bf2b294753","tid